      "widgets_values": [
        "Analyze the image and write a single rich prompt sentence packed with specific visual details.\n\n- 200 words minimum\n\nInclude ALL of the following that apply:\n- Character: skin tone, facial features, expression, makeup details, hair color/style/texture\n- Clothing: fabric, cut, colors, accessories, jewelry\n- Art style: illustration technique, line weight, shading style, influences\n- Color palette: dominant colors, contrast level, saturation\n- Composition: framing, background elements, decorative motifs\n- Mood and atmosphere \n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 41,
